  <summary>12/11/1987--Introduced.
Emergency Loan Extension and Adjustment Act of 1987 - Amends the Food Security Act of 1985 to make certain persons with 1987 crop damage eligible for emergency crop loans. Reduces such payments by any crop insurance premiums received.</summary>
